data.description: 2-story duplex! This model boasts 2 spacious Master Suite BDRMS, each w/ their own private bath & custom walk-in closets systems. Additionally, the model includes an upstairs loft, 9-foot ceilings on the first floor, & stylish 42-inch white kitchen cabinets paired & SS GE appliances that come included. The homes also feature LED surface mount lighting, modern two-panel doors with white columnist trim, & the latest in smart home connectivity features, including a Ring Video Doorbell Pro, Ring Alarm Security kit, myQ Smart Garage control, Flo by Moen Smart Water Shut-off system, & Honeywell smart thermostat. Enlarged patio with BBQ pad, perfect for outdoor living. Upgraded landscape with premium foliage. Located in the highly sought-after Crown Point school district & conveniently situated of I-65. Enjoy a short walk to a proposed park & can rest easy knowing that lawn care, snow removal, siding, and roof maintenance are all included w/ their monthly HOA fees. 3% assumable mortgage.
